data.description: Don’t miss your opportunity to be the next proud owner of this beautiful hm, highly sought-after Princess Anne Meadows community in VA Beach. Just built in 2021, home is just like new construction, but without waiting for new construction & without extra expenses you have when buying new construction. Current owner recently added the following improvements not included when purchased as new construction:refrig., W&D, blinds, fenced backyard, hardscape paver patio/firepit/sidewalk, custom-built closet storage. Very open & bright flr plan w/great flow. Tall ceilings & abundance of windows carries natural sunlight throughout! Gourmet kitchen w/lg island, prof. stainless appl., custom backsplash & quartz countertops that open to LR w/gas FP & sunrm. 2nd flr primary suite w/lg walk-in closet, luxurious BA w/tile shower, lg soaking tub, dbl sink vanity & beautiful marble flrs. Addit. rms; formal DR, sunrm, loft/flex-rm upstairs. Walk-in flred attic w/permanent stairs. 2 car attached garage
